Class MainHeader

java.lang.Object
com.github.junrar.rarfile.BaseBlock
com.github.junrar.rarfile.MainHeader
public class MainHeader
extends BaseBlock
The main header of an rar archive. holds information concerning the whole archive (solid, encrypted etc).
